      "index": 1,
      "title": "Accounting for Compromise Settlements",
      "summary": "MEC improperly recorded a transaction related to compromise settlements in Account 920, Administrative and General Salaries, instead of Account 426.5, Other Deductions. As a result, MEC included approximately $11,000 in its formula rate computation, and the revenue requirement used to set rates for wholesale customers was overstated.",
